# ─── Cycle.gg environment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Cycle.gg runs entirely client-side. The Riot API integration is BYO-key:
# each user supplies their own developer key via the in-app Settings page,
# and the key is stored in the user's own localStorage (never shipped by
# the server). Get a 24h dev key at https://developer.riotgames.com.
#
# ─── Optional: fallback Riot key for Cloudflare Pages Function ───────────
# If you self-host and want all visitors to use your key (at your risk),
# set this as a secret on your Pages project (not here):
#
#   wrangler pages secret put RIOT_API_KEY
#
# Do NOT put a real key in this file — .env is read by the dev server,
# and keys placed here in a VITE_ prefix will be bundled into the browser.
#
# ─── Optional: CORS origin for local dev ─────────────────────────────────
# Set when running the dev server against the deployed Pages Function.
# PAGES_CORS_ALLOW_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
